---
---
<section class="how-it-works" id="how-it-works">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="section-label">How it works</span>
    <h2>How <span class="mono-h">audit</span> works</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">One command. Four phases. Prioritized fix list.</p>

    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step" data-animate data-delay="0">
        <div class="step-left">
          <div class="step-num">1</div>
          <div class="step-connector"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <h4>Scan for secrets</h4>
          <p>Scans every file for 50+ secret patterns with entropy scoring. Respects <code>.gitignore</code> for build output but always scans <code>.env</code>, <code>.pem</code>, and other security-sensitive files.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step" data-animate data-delay="80">
        <div class="step-left">
          <div class="step-num">2</div>
          <div class="step-connector"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <h4>Run 13 security agents</h4>
          <p>Deploys specialized agents for injection, auth bypass, SSRF, supply chain, config, Supabase RLS, LLM security, mobile, git history, CI/CD, API fuzzing, and recon. Context-aware confidence tuning reduces false positives.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step" data-animate data-delay="160">
        <div class="step-left">
          <div class="step-num">3</div>
          <div class="step-connector"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <h4>Audit dependencies</h4>
          <p>Runs your package manager's own audit tool — npm, yarn, pnpm, pip, or bundler. Finds known CVEs in your dependency tree and flags vulnerable versions.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step" data-animate data-delay="240">
        <div class="step-left">
          <div class="step-num">4</div>
          <div class="step-connector"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <h4>Score &amp; remediation plan</h4>
          <p>Computes a 0–100 security score across 8 weighted categories. Generates a prioritized remediation plan — <span class="tag tag-red">CRITICAL</span> first, then <span class="tag tag-yellow">HIGH</span>, <span class="tag tag-gray">MEDIUM</span> — so you know exactly what to fix first.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step" data-animate data-delay="320">
        <div class="step-left">
          <div class="step-num">5</div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <h4>HTML report</h4>
          <p>Outputs a standalone dark-themed HTML report with every finding, file location, severity, CWE/OWASP mapping, and suggested fix. Share it with your team or attach it to a PR.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .mono-h {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    color: var(--cyan);
    font-size: 0.88em;
  }

  .steps {
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .step {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  .step-left {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .step-num {
    width: 2.2rem;
    height: 2.2rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--cyan);
    color: #09090b;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 0.1rem;
    box-shadow: 0 0 16px rgba(34,211,238,0.3);
  }

  .step-connector {
    width: 2px;
    flex: 1;
    min-height: 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--cyan-dim), rgba(14,116,144,0.1));
    margin: 0.4rem 0;
  }

  .step-body {
    padding-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .step:last-child .step-body { padding-bottom: 0; }

  .step-body h4 {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .step-body p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .step-body code {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    background: var(--cyan-glow);
    color: var(--cyan);
    padding: 0.1em 0.3em;
    border-radius: 3px;
    font-size: 0.85em;
  }

  .tag {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.1em 0.5em;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 0.78em;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .tag-red    { background: rgba(248,113,113,0.15); color: var(--red); border: 1px solid rgba(248,113,113,0.25); }
  .tag-yellow { background: rgba(251,191,36,0.12); color: var(--yellow); border: 1px solid rgba(251,191,36,0.25); }
  .tag-gray   { background: var(--bg-card); color: var(--text-muted); border: 1px solid var(--border); }
</style>
